    "sr_head": "Shipping",
    "sr_content": "<p><strong><br/>UK Delivery</strong></p><p>All UK deliveries are handled by either DPD or Royal Mail (customer choice) and include full tracking and delivery notifications.</p><p></p><p><strong>Standard Delivery - From £2.50</strong></p><p>Delivered within 2–5 working days.</p><p>Standard delivery pricing is calculated at checkout based on the weight of your order and the most suitable courier service.</p><p></p><p><strong>Next Day Delivery - From £3.50</strong></p><p>Order by 2pm, Monday to Friday (excluding Bank Holidays) for delivery on the next working day.</p><p>Multiple next day services are available at checkout, including timed options where applicable. Pricing is based on order weight and selected service.</p><p></p><p><strong>Free Next Day Delivery - Free on orders over £200</strong></p><p>Order by 2pm, Monday to Friday (excluding Bank Holidays) for delivery on the next working day.</p><p>Orders must be placed by 2pm (Monday–Friday, excluding Bank Holidays) to qualify for Next Day Delivery. </p><p>Orders placed after 2pm or on weekends/bank holidays will be processed on the next working day.</p><p><strong>Please note that Next Day Delivery is not available to certain locations and postcodes, including:</strong></p><p>ZE*, TR21–TR25, PH15–PH50, PA20–PA40, KW0–KW17, KA27–KA28, IV*, IM*, EI*, HS1–HS9, GY9–GY10, FK17–FK21, AB31–AB56.</p><p>For these areas, delivery typically takes 2–3 working days.</p><p>While we always aim to meet the delivery timeframes above, please note that all delivery times are estimates only. Marame cannot guarantee delivery by a specific date and accepts no liability for delays caused by courier services, weather conditions, incomplete or incorrect address details, customs, or other factors beyond our control.</p>",
    "returns_exchanges_policy": "<p>Returns from the UK can be processed using our free post DPD or Royal Mail service. We offer a paperless return option as well as the option to print your own postage label.</p><p>We accept returns within 30 days of fulfilment, items must be in their original condition, unworn/unwashed and unstained with all tags and labels still attached</p><p><strong>All returns are free of charge. You will be refunded the full amount you paid for the product you are returning. </strong></p><p>We also offer Exchanges, Store Credits and Instant Exchanges, where you can get your replacement product shipped out to you before we receive your return. We just take an authorisation hold on your card until your original product is received in good order. </p><p>Shipping charges are non-refundable. </p><p>Exchanges are available for different size, colours or completely different items. </p><p><strong>International returns have shipping fees which are detailed when submitting a return and vary by country. </strong></p>",
